title: Personal Saving for United States
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Two Variables--(1)--Original Data, 1939-1945 (2)--Seasonally Adjusted, 1945-1966. Raw Quarterly Figures Were Multiplied By Four To Derive Totals At Annual Rates. Data Are At Annual Rate. Source: U.S. Department Of Commerce, National Income, 1954 Edition, A Supplement To The Survey Of Current Business

This NBER data series q10091a appears on the NBER website in Chapter 10 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter10.html.
